<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1997699-as-an-atheist-and-relatively-new-convert">As an atheist and relatively new &quot;convert&quot; to meditation, I like the concept of this book. However, does it assume the reader already knows about Buddhism? 

I know nothing and would be lost if that assumption was made.</a>
